text:
Hey Millie!

Welcome back :) That's exciting that you are deciding to pursue photography! Asking a family friend who runs their own photography business seems like a great idea. Several friends of mine started out as a photography assistants, and that seems to have been a good starting point for each of them. What kinds of photography does your family friend do at their business?

I'll respond more specifically in the next day or so, just wanted to acknowledge that I got your message.
Thanks, no worries! They do portraits and nature photography so perfect for me.
